title: Kill Me Three Times. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: April 10th, 2015

Description:

A mercurial assassin (Simon Pegg) discovers he isn't the only person trying to kill the siren (Alice Braga) of a sun-drenched surfing town. In this darkly comedic thriller, the hitman finds himself unraveling three tales of mayhem, murder, blackmail and revenge.

Director: Kriv Stenders

Writers: James McFarland

Actors: Simon Pegg, Luke Hemsworth, Teresa Palmer, Sullivan Stapleton, Alice Braga, Callan Mulvey, Bryan Brown

Genre: Action and Adventure, Thriller
